Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.70,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}あの頃 ワタシたちは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:02.44,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}飛べないプロペラで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:06.90,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}空のもう半分見上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.01,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}裸足で走ってたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:14.45,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}ワタシたちはいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:21.54,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}勘違いだとか自信で生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:34.89,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}大事な宝物をね しまえるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:43.49,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}心　きっと見えなくなってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.49,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}ぐるぐる廻せ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.60,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}この魔法の杖で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:55.63,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}涙とSunny day 混ぜたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:59.34,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}淋しがりやさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.54,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢は叶うよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:10.87,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}いつだって　一緒だよ 私たち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:58.70,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:02.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}对着无法起飞的螺旋桨做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:06.90,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝着天空的另一半抬头望去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.01,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光着脚丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:14.45,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我们永远都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:21.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}无论误会与否 就是对生活充满自信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:34.89,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的宝物 藏起来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:43.49,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也无法发现那颗深藏起来的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.49,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕噜咕噜转上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.60,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用这根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:55.63,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼泪和晴天混合起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:59.34,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:01.54,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}梦想一定会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:10.87,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我们要永远在一起哦
